---
title: Firecracker Meatballs with Roasted Carrots & Sesame Rice
description: This recipe is here to blow up everything you think you know about meatballs. All dramatics aside, these meatballs are truly game-changing thanks to a certain onomatopoeic sauce. What exactly is “firecracker,” you ask? Well, mystery asker, it’s a creamy, spicy, sweet, and savory (yes, all those things!) sauce so good, it’ll make your taste buds explode! Once the meatballs are baked, they’re tossed in the magical condiment, then plated atop sesame-seed-flecked rice along with roasted carrots (AKA more things to dip in sauce). Don’t be surprised when you find yourself swiping up every last drop.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5ff4b6b93115cd6d2d317e6e-4503fc5b.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/firecracker-meatballs-5ff4b6b93115cd6d2d317e6e-8bdf7c50.pdf
course: main course
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/firecracker-meatballs-5ff4b6b93115cd6d2d317e6e
author: Michelle Doll Olson
time required: 40 minutes
cuisine: Asian
